  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/279b8394d9481cd783fe7df8f0b41a8f.poster.avif?t=1706211296\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/279b8394d9481cd783fe7df8f0b41a8f.webm?t=1706211296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/279b8394d9481cd783fe7df8f0b41a8f.mp4?t=1706211296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reasons why you shouldn’t camp at Sackwill</h2><br>Short answer is because its haunted but if you want to hear the truth behind Sackwill, take a seat. Evil lurks around every dark corner in these woods. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/1aa9c01cb404a6805b45bfdd377271b5.poster.avif?t=1706211296\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/1aa9c01cb404a6805b45bfdd377271b5.webm?t=1706211296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/1aa9c01cb404a6805b45bfdd377271b5.mp4?t=1706211296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Side-Scrolling Hack & Slash Puzzle</h2><br>Ressifice is a B-movie experience as a game. Put those neurons, at least few of them to work and figure out the puzzles to progress through this damned land. Use your \"Dodge/Duck\" button cautiously & mind your stamina. Beat the sack-head cultist to a bloody pulp with your thick crude wooden stick. It kinda looks like a baseball bat actually.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/5699330fe05b61c7f462032254d04d88.poster.avif?t=1706211296\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597090/extras/5699330fe05b61c7f462032254d04d88.webm?t=1706211296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
